Carnatron appeared behind Kit Kat. He placed a piece of his suit on her, it 
would heal her..but with about half the speed of a chamber so if she got hit 
enough it would kill her. "Take care young one, you have spirit but not much 
brains." Carnatron transformed into Rodimus and blasted away at the two bots.
> KitKat::
>

> warning flash across her optics. Her life meter was down to 30%. She 
> breathed hard, but kept firing. She would see victory or death this 
> day. To honor and the warrior code.
